OL,3,CTiger Woods was looking at phone
OL,4,Cbefore DUI crash, arrest report shows
OL,6,FTiger Woods had prescription
OL,7,Fpainkillers in his pocket and had been
OL,8,Flooking down at his phone before
OL,9,Fcrashing into another vehicle,
OL,10,Faccording to a sheriff's report.
OL,12,FThe professional golfer failed several
OL,13,Ffield sobriety tests following the
OL,14,Fcrash in Florida on Friday, the report
OL,15,Fdetailing his arrest showed.
OL,17,FThe 50-year-old was charged with
OL,18,Fdriving under the influence, and
OL,19,Freleased on bail in the early hours of
OL,20,FSaturday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/9
