OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1774991532
OL,3,CTiger Woods was looking at phone
OL,4,Cbefore DUI crash, arrest report shows
OL,6,FWoods told a sheriff's deputy he was
OL,7,Flooking down at his cell phone and
OL,8,Fchanging the radio station before he
OL,9,Fcrashed, and that he didn't notice the
OL,10,Fvehicle in front of him had slowed
OL,11,Fdown.
OL,13,FAccording to the arrest affidavit (a
OL,14,Fstatement written under oath), two
OL,15,Fwhite pills identified as hydrocodone
OL,16,Fwere found in Woods' trouser pocket
OL,17,Fduring a search after his arrest.
OL,19,FHydrocodone is a prescription opioid
OL,20,Fused to treat severe, chronic pain.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/9
