OL,3,CTiger Woods was looking at phone
OL,4,Cbefore DUI crash, arrest report shows
OL,6,FWoods told deputies he had consumed no
OL,7,Falcohol but said he takes "a few"
OL,8,Fprescription medications and had taken
OL,9,Fthem earlier that morning.
OL,11,FThe golf legend was driving a Land
OL,12,FRover when he clipped a pickup truck
OL,13,Fpulling a small trailer, Martin County
OL,14,FSheriff John Budensiek said last week,
OL,15,Fcausing Woods' SUV to roll onto its
OL,16,Fside.
OL,18,F"Our DUI investigators came to the
OL,19,Fscene here, and Mr Woods did exemplify
OL,20,Fthe signs of impairment," Budensiek
OL,21,Fsaid.
