OL,3,CTiger Woods was looking at phone
OL,4,Cbefore DUI crash, arrest report shows
OL,6,FThe 82-time PGA Tour winner was
OL,7,Fcharged with driving under the
OL,8,Finfluence, property damage and refusal
OL,9,Fto submit to a lawful test.
OL,11,FWoods was sweating profusely and had
OL,12,Fslow movements, bloodshot eyes and
OL,13,Fdilated pupils, a Martin County
OL,14,Fsheriff's deputy wrote in the
OL,15,Fstatement.
OL,17,FDue to Woods' physical limitations `
OL,18,Fhe told deputies he has had seven back
OL,19,Fsurgeries and more than 20 operations
OL,20,Fon his leg ` the tests were conducted
OL,21,Fwhile he was seated.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/9
