OL,3,CTiger Woods was looking at phone
OL,4,Cbefore DUI crash, arrest report shows
OL,6,FWoods made multiple errors, such as
OL,7,Fstarting exercises before being
OL,8,Finstructed to do so; not counting
OL,9,Fsteps correctly; and not returning his
OL,10,Fhand to his side as directed,
OL,11,Faccording to the statement.
OL,13,FThe deputy "believed that Woods'
OL,14,Fnormal faculties were impaired, and he
OL,15,Fwas unable to safely operate the motor
OL,16,Fvehicle," she wrote.
