OL,3,CTiger Woods was looking at phone
OL,4,Cbefore DUI crash, arrest report shows
OL,6,FA breath test administered at the
OL,7,FMartin County Jail registered 0.000 on
OL,8,Fboth samples, indicating no alcohol
OL,9,Fwas present.
OL,11,FWoods refused to submit to a urine
OL,12,Ftest to determine the presence of
OL,13,Fchemical or controlled substances.
OL,15,FThe circumstances of his arrest bore
OL,16,Fsimilarities to his 2017 arrest, after
OL,17,Fwhich prescription drugs were found in
OL,18,Fhis system, including hydrocodone.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/9
