OL,3,CTiger Woods was looking at phone
OL,4,Cbefore DUI crash, arrest report shows
OL,6,FWhether Woods returns to next month's
OL,7,FMasters Tournament remains in question
OL,8,Fafter the latest in a series of auto
OL,9,Fincidents dating back to 2009, when he
OL,10,Fwas cited for careless driving.
OL,12,FThe 15-time major winner pleaded
OL,13,Fguilty to reckless driving in 2017
OL,14,Fafter he was arrested that May on
OL,15,Fsuspicion of DUI.
OL,17,FHis 12-month probation was contingent
OL,18,Fon completing recommended treatment,
OL,19,Fincluding DUI school, 50 hours of
OL,20,Fcommunity service and random drug and
OL,21,Falcohol testing.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/9
