OL,3,CTiger Woods was looking at phone
OL,4,Cbefore DUI crash, arrest report shows
OL,6,FIn 2021, Woods was hospitalised after
OL,7,Fa serious rollover crash in Los
OL,8,FAngeles County that investigators
OL,9,Fruled was an accident.
OL,11,FSince then, he has played in 11
OL,12,Ftournaments but finished only four.
OL,14,FAsked last week about a return to
OL,15,Fcompetitive golf, Woods said he was
OL,16,F"trying," but his "body doesn't
OL,17,Frecover like when I was 24/25."
