OL,3,CTiger Woods was looking at phone
OL,4,Cbefore DUI crash, arrest report shows
OL,6,F"I've had a couple bad injuries here
OL,7,Fin the past year," Woods told
OL,8,Freporters after a TGL match. "I've had
OL,9,Fto fight through, it's taken some
OL,10,Ftime. But I keep trying. I want to
OL,11,Fplay."
